s=m><span class=title>   Re: Castlevania: White Night Concerto</span><hr size=1> I'm talking about White Night Concerto ... the subject of this thread.  I'm playing a rom of the import.<br><br>The game does not use the card system.  It's uses a combination of spellbooks and sub-weapons.  I've only two of the spell books ... not sure how many there actually are ... I didn't bother to count.  Any way, each spell book works in conjunction with your current sub-weapon.  Each weapon/spellbook combination has it's own special attack.  <br><br>Looking at the maps for the game I would hazard that it's a bit longer.  I'm assuming that the 40% I have right now is for the A map and does not count the B map.<br><br><br>Spyder - good luck trying to find SOTN.  I've been searching and it's a hard find.  You'll have to scour high and low and be diligent or you're not likely to ever get your hands on a copy. <p><br><br><center><font size=2><a href="http://pub80.ezboard.com/umercurialme.showPublicProfile">New profile!</a>   <font color=red>I'm FUN.   <a href="aim:goim?Screenname=anyterenee">Lets's CHAT d00d.  =)</a>   I'm FUN.  <a href="http://www.liquid2k.com/anyte">Webby!</a></font></center><br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/uspyders17.showPublicProfile?language=EN>spyders17</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(6/19/02 10:40:26 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=217.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.liquid2k.com/spyder17/luciferavatar2.gif width=125 height=115></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Castlevania: White Night Concerto</span><hr size=1> mercurial - actually, I just asked a friend, and he has it <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/